    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364460/extras/1cfede9e4937278bd128ed58c7a2a0b3.avif?t=1768398014\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An <strong>FPS</strong> starring your favorite platformer character <strong>Captain Moviestar</strong>… now in full <strong>three-dimensions</strong>. Early 90’s 2.5D-style raycaster-shooter inspired (<i>Wolfenstein 3D, Chub Gam 3D, Doom, Nite-mare 3D, Ken’s Labyrinth, Rise Of The Triad</i>), y-shearing, jumping, flood-fill sound propagation, 10 weapons, four difficulty modes and 5 episodes of moderately violent action. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364460/extras/b55f78d85fade0ede68cadfb47d41944.poster.avif?t=1768398014\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364460/extras/b55f78d85fade0ede68cadfb47d41944.webm?t=1768398014\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364460/extras/b55f78d85fade0ede68cadfb47d41944.mp4?t=1768398014\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364460/extras/a79d37b1bbd09c1a6e0b9de15d66681b.avif?t=1768398014\" width=662 height=148 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pound your keyboard, gamepad or joystick, scrub your 1-button mouse or trackpad and fight your way through hoards of evil demons, henchmen and monsters. Non-normalized movement vectors so you can strafe-run to speedrun success. Auto-aim so you can play with just arrow-keys, single-stick or d-pad. Localized translations for thirteen languages, so no matter where you are, you can understand what’s going on (or just shoot stuff). </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364460/extras/138f702a42a0cccf1827ae3700391a96.poster.avif?t=1768398014\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364460/extras/138f702a42a0cccf1827ae3700391a96.webm?t=1768398014\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364460/extras/138f702a42a0cccf1827ae3700391a96.mp4?t=1768398014\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364460/extras/6bada6ce9559a159f3a8712361e6a504.avif?t=1768398014\" width=608 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Module-based music, authentic 8-bit sound fx and 15fps particle effects to harass your ears and boggle your mind. 90-degree walls, slopes, environment contrast, reflective mirrors, underwater swimming and hazardous areas all in incredible, eye-popping 6-bit color. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364460/extras/27f551add9340eb369550478afbbec07.poster.avif?t=1768398014\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364460/extras/27f551add9340eb369550478afbbec07.webm?t=1768398014\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364460/extras/27f551add9340eb369550478afbbec07.mp4?t=1768398014\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364460/extras/1be7551d03a508bf1b70efdb6c6a1ace.avif?t=1768398014\" width=440 height=82 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364460/extras/ebb97ac40f82836da25276e764f8acda.poster.avif?t=1768398014\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364460/extras/ebb97ac40f82836da25276e764f8acda.webm?t=1768398014\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364460/extras/ebb97ac40f82836da25276e764f8acda.mp4?t=1768398014\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ten weapons (discluding melee), twenty monsters types, five challenging difficulties and much more planned.</p>",
